Welcome!

This dotfiles repository uses a combination of `git` and GNU `stow`. To use, simply clone:

    cd ~
    git clone <repo_url>
    cd <repo_dir>

From inside `~/<repo_dir>`, one may `stow` typical `$HOME` based configurations in the following manner:

    stow i3
    stow vim

And other configurations as follows:

    stow -t / root

